Subject: [PATCH 13/13] Update weird-asm snapshot for the C-comment
 missing-return warning

"Read COP0/GTE registers as expressions instead of erroring, add syscall op"
intentionally moved the missing-"jr $ra" warning from a stderr print into a C
comment so it survives in the generated source. It refreshed psx-gte-cop2s
snapshot but not weird-asms, leaving the e2e suite red.
